1.0.name: wordpress/jquery-slider
1.0.description:
This is a highly customizable jQuery Slider plugin. You can set its width, height, pagination and other parameters. You can use it on your post or page using schortcode [jQuery Slider] or in your template file using php function <?php if(function_exists('jquery_slider')){ jquery_slider(); } ?>.

Slides can be added as post type slide from slides menu.

For more details, please visit: http://www.iwebrays.com/
